																</div><!--mvp-author-box-out-->
																<div id="mvp-author-box-text" class="left relative">
																	<p>Raihan Ronodipuro was awarded the Chinese MOFCOM Scholarship and earned a Master of Law in International Relations from the School of International and Public Affairs at Jilin University in China. He is an independent research analyst specializing on Sino-Indonesian relations and Asia-Pacific issues.</p>
