															<h2 class="mvp-stand-title">Vietnam’s economy is forecast to grow by about 4.8 percent in 2021</h2>
															<p>Vietnam’s GDP is expected to expand by about 4.8 percent in 2021, although it has posted a robust economic performance...</p>
